  "What does 'rigid transformation' mean?": "",
  "A transformation that only stretches the graph": "",
  "A transformation that flips the graph over both axes": "",
  "A transformation that changes the shape of the graph": "",
  "A transformation that moves the graph without changing its size or shape": "",
  "A rigid transformation preserves the shape and size of the graph, only changing its position. Translations and reflections are rigid transformations, while stretches and compressions are not.": "",
